  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: <span class=3DSpellE>Gravitic</sp=
an>,
  Area-of-Effect, Ion<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Drushocka</span> evolved on=
 a world
  very prone to intense lightning storms, probably resulting in their desir=
e to
  control energy as best they can.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;
  </span>Physically they rather resemble a collection of boulders. They move
  through the oscillation of these moss fibers along their bodies.<o:p></o:=
p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Suffice to say, they move very slow. However, they m=
ake up
  for this in physical toughness. Since they are predominantly composed of
  silicate based materials, they are literally as tough as rock.<o:p></o:p>=
</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>It is believed that the <span class=3DSpellE>Drushoc=
ka</span>
  follow a dictatorial feudal system, with each lesser 'caste' swearing
  allegiance to a lord above it, and those lords swearing allegiance to a r=
uler
  who is chosen by the former ruler before he dies. The <span class=3DSpell=
E>Drushocka</span>
  are best characterized as inflexible and straightforward. They see a goal,
  they move towards it and they attain it.</p>
